sub_title: Marketing  & Commercial Strategy | Business Development | Strategic Partnerships | Brand Building | HEC Paris MBA Graduate
summary:
I'm a passionate marketing & sales professional and MBA graduate with 10+ years of experience working in business development, brand management, sales strategy and trade marketing across multiple geographies. I enjoy learning about people -  how to motivate, inspire and get the most of every member of my teams. I'm convinced that this, together with data driven insights are the key to create compelling strategies for happier and more satisfied consumers. 

After working 4+  years in Colombia developing comprehensive strategic plans for multi-channel brands such as Powerade, Fuze Tea and Del Valle, I decided to move out of my confort zone and embrace a growth and transformation journey in the Netherlands. This journey has included experience in consulting & business development in EU, LATAM and ASIA.  I'm proficient in four languages (SP,EN, FR, PT), hopefully my Dutch will be good enough soon to be added to this list. 

When I’m not bridging the gap between strategy and creativity, you could find me running in the closest park, challenging myself to go faster and farther than the day before.  I believe that as running life is about getting comfortable being uncomfortable. Thus, I constantly embrace challenging goals that push me to work hard, different and better!
